_project.description: This is the WR Any% No Amiibo Route
_project.name: Any% Route

_route: (==) Route follows these videos .link([1]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HwuPldbQIGo) & .link([2]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zai1rt8hK6A), also make sure to read notes.

.loc(SoR) + Clip.notes: Remember to set Language to French for fastest text. .link([Check Link's camera and angle in minimap during clip. Reload page for image.]data:image/png;base64,)

.loc(Temple of Time) Clip.comment: After clip, grab bow in chest.

.loc(Bombs Shrine) + Clip.comment: Clip in on right side of shrine.

Inside .loc(Shrine).notes: Quick Fix by Shield Jumping + Unequip. At end of shrine wait for monk to finish, bc loading time.

BLSS to .loc(Mag Shrine).notes: Clear Skew, then BLSS off of the wall on the right of you/the north wall

Inside .loc(Shrine).notes: Go through the shrine normally, shield surf over the gap at the end, strafe so guardian doesn't hit you, before exiting, blow self up to get rid of glitched ragdoll state.

BLSS to .loc(Tree) + Windbomb.comment: BLSS off wall on your left.

Inside Shrine.notes: Go through shrine normally, cancel stasis animation by pressing R or Y afterwards, shield surf over gap at the end.

Boulder Ride up to BLSS.notes: 10 hits requires a fall damage cancel.

BLSS to .loc(Cryo Shrine).notes: Check 1st video at 11:33 for precise setup

.loc(Cryo Shrine) + Clip.notes: Go to song's clip tutorial in desc. of 1st video for precise setup.
